                     <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="t18000709-76-defend562 t18000709-76-punish397"></join>
               Confined twelve months in the House of Correction
            </rs>, and <rs id="t18000709-76-punish398" type="punishmentDescription">
